      • insert

        AppUser insert(AppUser appUser)
        throws javax.persistence.RollbackException
        Inserts a new AppUser given that its username is unique. The insertion generates the user's id.
        Parameters:
        appUser - The object to persist.
        Returns:
        Returns the AppUser, updated with its new id.
        Throws:
        javax.persistence.RollbackException - Thrown when a primary or unique key already exists in the database.
